('Exactly Accountancy', 'Tax/Accounting', 'Five-star online tax and accounting firm specializing in services for expats throughout Spain. AECE-certified accountants providing comprehensive services including bookkeeping, tax returns, business formation (SL company setup), autónomo registration, and insurance services. Offers dedicated support in English, Dutch, and Spanish with a modern, proactive approach. All services delivered online through a digital platform with mobile document submission. Features an online financial dashboard for business clients. Accredited member of the Association of Accountants and Tax Advisors in Spain (AECE) and affiliated with the Spanish Tax Agency (Agencia Tributaria). Also recognized as an Odoo Gold Accounting & Finance Partner. Serves clients across all of Spain remotely. Main customer base from the UK and The Netherlands.', 'Calle Punta Albir s/n, 03590 Altea', 'Altea', 'Alicante', '+34 965 020 262', 'support@exactly.es', 'https://www.exactly.es', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
